SUMMARY:Summer Fete
DESCRIPTION:Our annual Summer Fete on the Hut grounds — bouncy castle\, BBQ\, raffle\, plus a chance for parents to meet the leadership team and learn about the year ahead.\nVolunteers welcome — get in touch if you can help with the BBQ or the gates rota.\n
